reviewText: Sucked!  No volume to it.  Threw it out.
Victor Borge is very funny in this video, good comedy last forever, and he is the best

I was glad that I found this because I really enjoy watching him perform, my mom also enjoys him, so I was able to find this on line and I was able to use my gift card to purchase it Thanks for making my gift shopping so easy this year, I will probably be using you in the future to purchase hard to find gifts.
